                                "Snare Drum Top & Guitar Cabs",
                                "Studio Lead Vocals & Room Mics",
                                "Drum Overheads & Acoustic Guitars",
                                "Inside the Kick Drum Shell"
                            ],
                            "rationale": "Dynamic mics are tough and handle loud sound like snare and amps. Large Condensers capture warm, detailed vocals. Small Condensers are fast and bright, ideal for cymbals and acoustic guitars."
